{"tid":515280,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又一艘香港籍貨船涉嫌載石油給北韓遭南韓扣押！ 船員多為中國人","createTime":"2017-12-31T09:47:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-03T03:36:19.000Z","uid":35790,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"0a9ed50a820179dc47cc09aa64b62f7ee6e77a0b","tid":515280,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T09:47:32.000Z","msg":"又一艘船涉嫌載石油給北韓！船員多為中國、緬甸人<br />\n<br />\n2017-12-31 16:11<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕載有23名中國船員的香港籍船隻「Lighthouse Winmore（方向永嘉）」，因為載送油料給北韓而遭南韓扣押，如今又有船隻涉嫌為北韓偷運石油！南韓海關官員指出，目前已扣押一艘掛有巴拿馬旗幟的貨船「KOTI」，船員大多來自中國和緬甸。<br />\n據《路透》報導，KOTI可載運5100噸石油，南韓當局於平澤唐津港口扣押該船，海關與情報單位已進行聯合調查，KOTI涉嫌向北韓轉移石油的行為，已違反國際制裁的規定。<br />\n目前並不清楚南韓是何時展開扣押行動，但這已是短期內第二起事件。方向永嘉因為在公海上轉移600噸油品給北韓船隻「Sam Jong2」，於11月24日遭南韓扣押。<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2298905\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2298905&d=gqsARO6j01kn80G1UzvT3NtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=e5826bc2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2298905&h=23fc5226\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2298905</a>"},{"pid":"3977a335731838eb1852b853b5ae0d266633fea3","tid":515280,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T09:50:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acac62b623d0e094197a86175f6884a44efb9ffc","tid":515280,"uid":25858,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T09:51:14.000Z","msg":"condom港<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8efc2c8ba0a9674af3fde35db4eebccf87c0b2c0","tid":515280,"uid":4574,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T09:51:23.000Z","msg":"整撚臭香港個名<br />\n仆街支那賤種<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cec1a84d28f63f89088f1ebfa91f12f5c12bb55e","tid":515280,"uid":34869,"like":26,"dislike